Author: EzraCelestine
Text: Godddddd the "tips" are so fucking triggering. One of the nurses in the psych ward I just got out of saw "disordered eating" on my chart and legit like. Printed out the fuckin food pyramid and a "symptoms of disordered eating" list and made me sit theough an hour of her telling me that it wasn't healthy. Like. Thanks, Cathy, I *was* gonna eat some of my dinner tonight but I think I'll just cry for a few hours and not eat until lunch tomorrow :)
